com.ibm.ecm.api.coresdk.constants

Enum IBMECMPrivilege

  • Object
    • Enum<IBMECMPrivilege>
      • IBMECMPrivilege
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<IBMECMPrivilege>

    public enum IBMECMPrivilege
extends Enum<IBMECMPrivilege>
    An enumeration of privileges in a repository.

    A privilege is an access right or permission that describes what the current user can do to an item.
